[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 3.7.1"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 3.7.1 are now fixed in Tails 3.8.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.8|news/version_3.8]] as soon as possible.

 - Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2018-17]]
 - Enigmail: [[!cve CVE-2018-12020]], [[!cve CVE-2018-12019]]
 - libgcrypt [[!debsa2018 4231]]
 - perl [[!debsa2018 4226]]
